data.description: Beautiful brick ranch with 3 large bedrooms,2.5 baths.  Cathedral ceilings. Tile and engineered hardwood flooring.  Full poured finished basement.  Triple pane windows.  Updates include roof, shed, closet organizers, pantry, storm doors, water heater, breaker box & electrical supply meter 2016-2017.  Refrigerator 2020.  AC 2023. Main floor laundry.  So much to enjoy, come see this wonderful home.  Please allow 24 hour notice for showing.
